item.dc:creator: @l_o_l l o l
item.description:
@l_o_l wrote:

I don’t think the change from ::char is permanent in any server.I have the command and it didn’t save for me.

And for your other question. Open up client.java and search for

 /*END OF DROP*/

And you should see something like

/*END OF DROP*/ sendQuest("Noooo! Don't go! Please!", 2450); sendQuest("Ah well, click the button vv..", 2451); sendQuest("Thanks for coming.", 2452); if (playerName.equalsIgnoreCase("topknight18")) {

Change what it says after sendQuest[br][size=1]Posted at: 10 October 2006, 00:37:29[/size][hr]Don’t delete the brackets or the " " things.
